    // to 1.02 when `orientation` is *v* and 0.5 when `orientation` is *h*. When `xref` is *container*, defaults to *1*
    // when `orientation` is *v* and 0.5 when `orientation` is *h*. Must be between *0* and *1* if `xref` is *container*
